Add the auto-label workflow to your repository's `.github/workflows/` directory. The action requires no configuration when your repository uses standard npm/Bun workspaces ŌĆö it automatically detects your package scope and workspace structure. For non-standard setups, you can override the label prefix with the `label-prefix` input parameter.


