### Release PR approval flow
Release PRs now properly trigger auto-approval by using different identities for the PR author and reviewer. Previously, release PRs were stuck because GitHub prevents users from approving their own PRs ŌĆö the bot was trying to approve PRs it created itself.

## ŌÜÖ’ĖÅ Configuration Required

