The orchestrator reads `package.json` `agents.rules` and delegates to one stack skill:

| `agents.rules` value                     | Stack skill                          |
| ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `Bun` ┬Ę `Bun+React+Tailwind`             | `Skill(autopilot:plan-bun)`          |
